title: Giant Spenders and Skittish Colts
description:
Mina and Jonathan Jones of CBS discuss why they like what the Bills and Jets did in free agency, whether or not the Washington Football Team and New York Giants did enough to compete with the Cowboys in the NFC East, and why the NFC West is an apocalyptic hellscape.
